## Overview
If you are new to **Blueprints** in Unreal Engine 4, this **Blueprint - How To** series will provide information on the core aspects needed to working with Blueprints including Basic Usage, Adding and Connecting Nodes, Creating Variables and others as seen in the table below. 

When you are ready and have an understanding of the core aspects behind Blueprints, **Gameplay** oriented How To's can be found in the [](Gameplay) which illustrate gameplay related elements like Spawning/Destroying Actors, Respawning (OnDestroyed), Using Timers, and more. 

